      • DUALIZE_KEY

        public static final java.lang.String DUALIZE_KEY
        Key for boolean property. If true, the IPM will dualize the conic program before solving it. The IPM will substitute the results back into the original problem, so this should only affect the computational cost of #solve(ConicProgram), not the quality of the solution.
        See Also:
        Dualizer, Constant Field Values
